Insertion Sort is a room.

To insertion sort (arr - a list of numbers):
    let n be the number of entries in arr;
    repeat with i running from 2 to n:
        let key be entry i of arr;
        let j be i minus 1;
        while j >= 1 and entry j of arr > key:
            now entry (j + 1) of arr is entry j of arr;
            decrease j by 1;
        now entry (j + 1) of arr is key.

When play begins:
    let data be {5, 3, 1, 4, 2};
    insertion sort data;
    say "[data].";
